<l>muṟpaṭak kiḷanta vurupiya ṉilaiyum</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The word <foreign xml:lang="ta">veyil</foreign> ' heat ' follows the behaviour of <foreign xml:lang="ta">maḻai</foreign> ' rain '.<note
